    • Method Detail

      • execute

        public void execute()
        In this method the Node is created/ invoked into the model tree through setting it's boundaries and Container. Because in this command a Compartment/Grouping is created it's child Rolemodel must be setted as well .
        Overrides:
        execute in class ORMNodeCreateCommand

      • undo

        public void undo()
        This command is undone through removing the created Node from the the Container and deleting it's boundaries. Because in this command a Compartment is created it's child Rolemodel must be removed as well .

        undo in class ORMNodeCreateCommand
